title: Trailer Wiring Install: CURT 56016 on a Mazda CX-9
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 56016 custom vehicle-to-trailer wiring harness on the 2008 Mazda CX-9. You must read and understand the supplied instruction sheet(s) prior to installing. 


Instruction Sheet:
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/56016/installsheet/CME_56016_INS.PDF


Application Coverage:
2011-2014 Mazda 2
2007-2015 CX-9
2006-2012 Mazda 5


Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
tags: CURT Receiver Hitch, Trailer hitch, towing, how to install, Mazda CX-9, Mazda 5, Mazda 2
